data.description: Welcome to 440 Road 5138 in Cleveland TX! This attractive property features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing a comfortable living space for you and your family. The open floor plan connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining. The bedrooms are spacious. The backyard offers plenty of room for outdoor activities. Conveniently located near amenities, schools, and parks, this home is a great place to call your own. Contact us today to schedule a showing
